University Catering

Hosting your wedding on the University of Iowa campus or anywhere in the Iowa City area provides you with a variety of distinguished and historical venues, superior planning services, and fine dining options—all with a host of amenities to help you in preparing for the big day. 

By booking your wedding through University Catering, you package some of the largest challenges of planning your day. Our experienced wedding coordinators will take the weight off your shoulders as we guide you through the planning process.

View the wedding menus

From the grandeur of the Iowa Memorial Union’s Main Lounge to the panoramic views from Kinnick Stadium’s Paul W. Brechler Press Box, you and your guests are ensured a memorable wedding day that only the UI campus can provide. Our locations can comfortably suit any size event, from intimate venues like the Old Capitol and Old Brick Auditorium, to larger venues like Kinnick Stadium’s Paul W. Brechler Press Box and the Iowa Memorial Union .
